Paper: hep-th/0106060

Date: 2001-06-07

Title: Causal Poisson Brackets of the SL(2,R) WZNW Model and its Coset Theories

Authors: C. Ford, G. Jorjadze and G. Weigt

Comments: 7 pages, LaTeX, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B514 (2001) 413-416

From the basic chiral and anti-chiral Poisson bracket algebra of the SL(2,R)WZNW model, non-equal time Poisson brackets are derived. Through Hamiltonianreduction we deduce the corresponding brackets for its coset theories.